DOKO BUNNE SONG LYRICS :- 

Hookline :- 
Doko Bunne Nigalo Choyale
Jyanai Khayo Tyo Timro Moyale

Bhetinai Chhode Hajur Bar Pipal Chhaya
Uhile ta Lekhinthyo re Chithimaa Maya

Nachna Gauna Rodhimai Gayinthyo ni hai
Sathi sangi sabai chhute kaha gaya khoi
Sailiko tyo bolima adkinthyo man
Samjhana bhai bilai gaya ramaila ti chhen

Chhoto Jiwan Sang Sangai Hasaula
Nalau Pirim chhodera Janebhaa

Pahile Pahile ta Maya Lambhanda Gharkale dinthena re
Ahile ahile ta jali chhan sabai chokai mayai bhetinna re

Samjhana Sati Mayako Chino Kusume Rumal
Lairakhe Saili Nabirsiyos Maya Yo Jyanlai Sochera

Lu hai Manungkotaima mero dil basyo lali othaimaa.
Lu hai manung kotaima najar nalagau lali othaima.

Pirati lam na ta Saili ghumna lai jamna ta.
Pirati launna ma Saila ekdine pauna sa.

Oi hoi damauli katesi madiko pool hitaiko mayalai gulab ko phool.

Ghara mero rukumai timi Mam pareu ukhumai.
Ghar mero tanahu ho launa ke bhanam bhanam bho.

Na rup maa khot timro sundar gulabi otha timro.

Tan ramro Mam ramro timi lajauda jhan ramro.
Jiu pani kasilo timro muharai hasilo.

snippet.title: VEK X Oshin Karki - Pari Katha (Prod. by SNJV ) (ClassX Rush Live Track 2)
snippet.description:
ClassX Rush - Live Track No. 2 

From hearing her voice on an Instagram Live to finally creating together this truly feels like a dream come true.

In this episode of ClassX RUSH - LIVE, watch and listen as Oshin and I craft a complete track from scratch in just 3 hours and 13 minutes. From the first idea to writing every word, shaping melodies, and building the final sound.

This session captures the beauty of spontaneous creativity, collaboration, and trusting the process.
I want to extend a huge thank you to our extremely talented producers, SNJV and POZOD, who played a major role in creating this masterpiece.
Much love as well to my brothers KEEMA , NIXDII and SAGE for the incredible company and energy throughout the session. ü§ç

ClassX RUSH - LIVE is a space where ideas turn into music and artists come together to create without boundaries. This is only the beginning many more exciting artists will be joining this journey very soon.

snippet.title: Sajjan Raj Vaidya - Patra [Official Release]
snippet.description:
Letters within letters to let her know, that in all of my loving she is all I‚Äôve known. For when the night falls, and thoughts surround you and force a conversation, you realise neither time nor space can create distance from her of any kind. And so each day becomes a mere addition to how long you‚Äôve spent missing her. Each morning becomes a promise to face another night, once more, belonging to only her.
___________________________________________

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

snippet.title: Rze- Gimme The Loot x Manas Ghale(PROD BY SHIGU)
snippet.description:
BLACKHOUSEMOB presents Gimme The Loot From The album RZE (RUTHLESS ZONE)

By yourz truly RZE

This video is a music video for the song "Gimme The Loot" by RZE and Manash Ghale, produced by Shigu. The song is from RZE's album "RUTHLESS ZONE." The video features RZE and Manash Ghale performing the song, which has a hip-hop/rap style with lyrics about street life and asserting dominance (0:42-1:02, 1:31-1:53). The phrase "Give me the loot" is a prominent hook throughout the song (1:16-1:28, 2:16-2:20, 3:23-3:34). The video credits Jenish Maharjan as the director, Risheek Pradhan as the creative director, and features visuals by NFTP.

Bruno Mars is a 16x GRAMMY¬Æ-winning global superstar, singer, songwriter, multi-instrumentalist, producer, and one of the most-streamed artists in the world. Known for his showmanship and chart-toppers, Bruno has set a number of records throughout his career, including becoming the first artist ever to hit 150 million monthly listeners on Spotify, appearing on two of the fastest songs to reach one billion streams (for ‚ÄúDie with a Smile‚Äù with Lady Gaga and ‚ÄúAPT.‚Äù with ROS√â, and achieving the highest-certified song in RIAA history with 2010‚Äôs ‚ÄúJust the Way You Are‚Äù). Since launching a string of hits beginning in 2009, Bruno has sold over 150 million records worldwide, making him one of the best-selling artists of all time. Beyond his work as a soloist, Bruno is a member of the duo Silk Sonic with Anderson .Paak. In addition to his 35 Billboard Hot 100 hits, including nine number one singles, Bruno is the recipient of 16 GRAMMY¬Æ Awards (including ‚ÄúAlbum of the Year‚Äù for 24K Magic), 14 American Music Awards, and seven MTV Video Music Awards. His 24K Magic World Tour was among the highest-grossing tours in history, and within the top ten highest-grossing of the 2010s.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.description:
Arijit gave us a special gift in 2026 with a brand new version of ‚ÄòSukoon‚Äô and some magical runs which you‚Äôve not heard before ‚ù§Ô∏è

Lyrics:
Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 
Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 

Jo qudrat ne bikhere the
Bas meri raahon mein
Aur qismat ne sajaaye the
Meri nigaahon mein

Jaane ab kahaan milega 
Kahaan chhupa hoga 
Mil jaata toh rakh leta main
Apni panaahon mein

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Jhaank loon khud mein zara, sab kuch hai andar mere
Lehron pe milta nahin, jo gehre samandar mile 
Mehsoos hoga mujhe, jab khudko pehchanunga
Dil ke andar dekh kar, apni rooh ko jaanunga

Doobega‚Ä¶ Doobega‚Ä¶

Doobega toh tar jaaega
Har zarra mera
Varna tadap ke hi guzrega
Roz marra mera

Kya maine kabhi kiya hai
Thoda ishq bhi khudse 
Mil jaayega phir jo dhoondta hun 
Main darbadar kabse

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai
Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Woh sukoon mujhse hai‚Ä¶
Mujh mein hai sukoon‚Ä¶

snippet.title: She & Him - I Thought I Saw Your Face Today (Official Lyric Video)
snippet.description:
The official lyric video for "I Thought I Saw Your Face Today" by She & Him from the album 'Volume One' released on Merge Records

Subscribe To She & Him on YouTube: 
https://www.youtube.com/@SheandHimOfficial?sub_confirmation=1

Follow She & Him: 
http://www.sheandhim.com
http://www.instagram.com/sheandhim
http://www.facebook.com/sheandhim
http://www.twitter.com/sheandhim

Stream on Spotify:  https://bit.ly/ITISYFTSpotify
Stream on Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/song/i-thought-i-saw-your-face-today/1839131590
Stream on YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/ITISYFTYTMusic
Buy Vol. 1 on Vinyl: https://sheandhim.shop.redstarmerch.com/product/XZLPSH05/she-him-vol-1

Lyrics: 
I thought I saw your face today
But I just turned my head away
Your face against the trees
But I just see the memories
As they come, as they come

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again

I saw it glitter as I grew
And loved it, boy, I never knew
I thought this place was heaven-sent
But now it's just a monument
In my mind, in my mind

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again

The cars and freeways implore me to stay away, out of this place
My mother said, "Just keep your head, and play it as it lays"
The cars and freeways implore me to stay away, out of this place
My mother said, "Just keep your head, and play it as it lays"

I somehow see what's beautiful
In things that are ephemeral
I'm my only friend of mine
And love is just a piece of time
In the world, in the world

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall...

#SheAndHim #IThoughtISawYourFaceToday

snippet.title: Darling Maeju - Preezol Nepali | Official music video | Unisha Sherpa Deshar | Jyasa Films
snippet.description:
This song tells the story of love at first sight, a powerful and unforgettable feeling that transcends culture. Though I'm not Newar, I wanted to express my personal experience through the beauty of Newari language and music. It‚Äôs a celebration of love, connection, and that magical moment when everything changes. Whether you're familiar with Newari culture or not, love is universal. This track is a tribute to the emotions we all share. I hope it resonates with anyone who has ever experienced that instant spark.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#NessFitGamer #gta 5 #gta5hindi #gta5mods 

Franklin Traps EVERY GHOST Inside Evil Watch in Indian Bike Driving 3D! üò±

This video is about the Indian Bike Driving 3D game. It is a horror scary story about an Evil Watch (Magical Watch) in Indian Bike Driving 3D. In this scary story, Shinchan gets trapped inside the Evil Watch, and many ghosts and monsters like Granny, Huggy Wuggy, Mr. Meat, Choo-Choo Charles, Ice Scream Rod, and Evil Nun are released from it. To save Shinchan, Franklin must trap all the ghosts back inside the Evil Watch. Will Franklin be able to save Shinchan or not? Watch the full scary story to find out!

snippet.title: Mauni Amavasya 2026 Spiritual Snan | Narayan Narayan Hari Hari Dhun | Vishnu Ji
snippet.description:
#MauniAmavasya2026 #MauniAmavasyaSnan #ShreemanNarayan
Mauni Amavasya Snan 2026 is one of the most sacred days for spiritual purification and devotion to Lord Vishnu.
On this holy occasion of Mauni Amavasya 2026, listening to Shreeman Narayan Narayan Hari Hari Dhun brings peace, positivity, and divine blessings.
This powerful Lord Vishnu Ji Bhajan is ideal for Mauni Amavasya Ganga Snan, morning meditation, puja, and spiritual chanting.
Mauni Amavasya Snan is believed to wash away sins and grant moksha when combined with Vishnu Bhakti and Narayan mantra jap.
Experience the divine vibrations of Shreeman Narayan Hari Hari dhun specially curated for Mauni Amavasya Special 2026.
This devotional bhajan helps in meditation, stress relief, and connecting deeply with Lord Vishnu Ji.
Play this bhajan during Mauni Amavasya Snan, puja vidhi, or while doing Narayan jap for spiritual growth.
The peaceful Vishnu bhajan and Narayan dhun create a calm and sacred environment for devotion.
This Mauni Amavasya 2026 bhajan is perfect for devotees seeking blessings, inner peace, and divine energy.
May Lord Vishnu and Shreeman Narayan bless you with happiness, health, and spiritual upliftment.
